  "3292470": {
    "name": "湮灭之潮",
    "steam_appid": 3292470,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/b340df3734a26dd935bc9735c13468c3.poster.avif?t=1764067359\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/b340df3734a26dd935bc9735c13468c3.webm?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/b340df3734a26dd935bc9735c13468c3.mp4?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现实世界因遭到了异世界的突然入侵而变得支离破碎。作为这场灾难的唯一的幸存者格雯德琳，你将在现实与幻想交织的破碎伦敦中展开冒险，挑战来自异界的敌人，揭开这个世界的秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从湮灭的悬崖边，挽救遭受异世界入侵的现实伦敦</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来源未知的异世界突然入侵了现实伦敦。生命体被异化为无机物；街道与地标建筑被侵蚀扭曲呈现出奇异的样貌；整个城市被拉扯、切碎，即将与异世界融合在一起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为灾难中的幸存者，你将直面异世界的入侵，体验到丰富的关卡探索内容，揭示异世界降临的秘密，并找到挽救家人、城市甚至整个现实世界的办法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/6b97785bcb51af0725e4e068b05a57a1.poster.avif?t=1764067359\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/6b97785bcb51af0725e4e068b05a57a1.webm?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/6b97785bcb51af0725e4e068b05a57a1.mp4?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收获骑士之力，构建自己的骑士团</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >骑士战斗系统是游戏的创新设定，你可以在游戏中收获十种以上的独特骑士，这些来自亚瑟王传说的著名骑士们将与你并肩作战，他们都有着自己独特的角色定位——无论是冲击战斗，防御攻击，还是释放毁灭性的连击等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以根据战斗需求或者个人喜好进行对你的骑士团进行搭配组合，构建出丰富的战斗Build，不仅带来变化多端的动作连携，还能提供特殊的战斗策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将建立全新的战场态势，从此不再孤身作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/cc08228e6acb3161a027a58d802ef10f.poster.avif?t=1764067359\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/cc08228e6acb3161a027a58d802ef10f.webm?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/cc08228e6acb3161a027a58d802ef10f.mp4?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与奇观般的巨像骑士在世界中相遇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >庞大如高山一般的巨像骑士出现在两个世界中，他们并不是单纯的视觉奇观；你不仅将同他们进行史诗般的战斗，也可以攀登它们巨大的表面，探索它们内部的宫殿，去了解他们背后伟大的故事；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巨像骑士们将为你的战斗与关卡体验增添新的规模和奇迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/0fc537cc7fd89379f7bec1706b8db049.poster.avif?t=1764067359\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/0fc537cc7fd89379f7bec1706b8db049.webm?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292470/extras/0fc537cc7fd89379f7bec1706b8db049.mp4?t=1764067359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
